Privacy & Policy
By using the app, you agree to comply with the terms and conditions stated in this Privacy Policy.
Collection of personal information:
We do not collect, use, or store your personal information through the app. We do not require you to provide any personal information to use the app.
Data collection:
We may collect non-personal and non-identifiable information to provide and improve the user experience in the app. These types of information may include, but are not limited to, information about your device, operating system, app version, app usage activity, and other statistics related to app usage.
