Updating the Privacy Policy:
We may update this Privacy Policy over time. Any changes to this Privacy Policy will be published on our website or through the app. By continuing to use the app after these changes are posted, you acknowledge and agree to the updated Privacy Policy.
Contact:
If you have any questions or concerns regarding our Privacy Policy or the use of the app for, please contact us at the following email address: kingenglishkidsapp@gmail.com.